nodes.text: TK-8332 was the designation of a stormtrooper who served in Darth Vader's personal stormtrooper legion, Vader's Fist. After TK-4601 requested permission to transfer to the active-duty unit during the remainder of the battle aboard the Tantive IV, TK-8332 and TK-7624 were sent to escort Princess Leia Organa to Darth Vader.
